Good for Madison.

01:23.989 --> 01:25.432
Could be good for you too.

01:26.569 --> 01:28.419
Maybe she could get you on the squad.

01:28.449 --> 01:29.882
I'm not interested.

01:29.959 --> 01:32.289
Aw, come on, you'd look so cute

01:32.369 --> 01:33.919
in one of those little outfits.

01:34.409 --> 01:35.459
Never gonna happen.

