Sarah, no, you're
not, I said stop, okay.

25:00.576 --> 25:02.676
Put your hands back on the steering wheel.

25:03.259 --> 25:05.192
Put your hands on the wheel.

25:05.209 --> 25:07.309
Just calm down, is your foot on the brake?

25:07.619 --> 25:08.450
Yes.

25:08.452 --> 25:09.587
