25:14.455 --> 25:15.286
God.

25:15.288 --> 25:16.121
Are you ready?

25:16.269 --> 25:17.332
Okay, now go.

25:22.229 --> 25:23.147
Perfect, perfect.

25:23.149 --> 25:24.122
Are you all right?

25:24.179 --> 25:26.632
No, I don't, no, I
don't wanna drive anymore.

25:26.649 --> 25:27.577
Hey, hey, hey, okay, up here,

25:27.579 --> 25:28.822
just pull in up here.

25:29.079 --> 25:30.229
Just pull in over here.

25:38.619 --> 25:39.469
That was awful.

25:39.479 --> 25:41.079
Hey, hey, these things happen,

25:41.229 --> 25:42.629
that's why we're doing this.

25:42.919 --> 25:44.069
Look at me, look at me.

25:45.639 --> 25:48.087
I'm sorry that I yelled
at you, I didn't mean to.

25:48.089 --> 25:48.922
Okay?

26:07.686 --> 26:08.517
I'm sorry, I didn't mean to.

26:08.519 --> 26:11.852
Can you please just, Sarah, please.

26:14.086 --> 26:16.169
Just get back in the car.

26:17.027 --> 26:18.613
Get back in the car.

26:48.434 --> 26:50.267
Put your seat belt on.

27:29.532 --> 27:31.449
So this is my attempt to look

27:33.009 --> 27:34.132
sexy for

27:35.979 --> 27:36.832
you know who.

27:38.039 --> 27:40.712
Outfit of the day, as they say.

27:41.759 --> 27:43.279
Hashtag OOTD.

27:47.529 --> 27:48.702
You look nice.

27:50.109 --> 27:50.942
