27:54.589 --> 27:55.522
I need a ride.

27:56.839 --> 27:58.312
What is Vince's deal?

27:58.659 --> 27:59.609
What do you mean?

27:59.779 --> 28:01.479
What happened to his girlfriend?

28:01.619 --> 28:02.452
I don't know.

28:03.609 --> 28:05.142
What, don't you guys talk?

28:05.609 --> 28:08.252
Yeah, but not about stuff like that.

28:08.739 --> 28:09.989
What do you talk about?

28:10.649 --> 28:12.062
Like art,

28:12.239 --> 28:13.522
travel,

28:13.839 --> 28:15.489
he said he almost moved to Spain.

28:15.875 --> 28:19.282
Oh, no wonder he's single.

28:20.229 --> 28:21.179
What do you mean?

28:21.239 --> 28:24.012
Well, gallivanting all around Europe,

28:24.179 --> 28:25.792
instead of settling down.

28:26.299 --> 28:28.392
Maybe he's not ready to settle down.

28:29.017 --> 28:30.232
He's almost 40.

28:30.619 --> 28:33.187
So? Not everyone feels the same way

28:33.189 --> 28:35.142
about timelines as you do.

28:35.729 --> 28:37.329
You don't have to protect him.

28:37.529 --> 28:38.852
I'm not judging him.

28:39.499 --> 28:41.342
You judge everyone.

28:41.889 --> 28:43.842
Nancy, the doctor will see you now.

28:43.939 --> 28:45.082
Oh, thank you.

28:45.609 --> 28:46.440
Nice to see you.

28:46.442 --> 28:47.275
You too.

28:58.259 --> 28:59.092
Sarah?

29:01.314 --> 29:02.731
Okay, right here.

29:03.632 --> 29:05.357
I'm so excited,
I can't wait to see...

29:05.359 --> 29:06.882
Hi, sweetie.

29:07.169 --> 29:08.162
I'm Dr. Burke.

29:09.679 --> 29:10.512
Hi.

29:11.579 --> 29:12.602
Are you okay?

29:13.109 --> 29:14.159
Of course, sweetie.

29:14.819 --> 29:17.152
You have a very hip mother.

29:18.689 --> 29:20.737
I finally figured out what to give you

29:20.739 --> 29:22.342
for your graduation gift.

29:22.699 --> 29:24.712
Grad, it's not for a while.

29:24.859 --> 29:25.809
Why wait?

29:27.559 --> 29:29.362
Okay, what is it?

29:30.639 --> 29:31.472
Guess.

29:32.469 --> 29:33.302
A car?

29:33.579 --> 29:34.412
No.

29:36.018 --> 29:37.312
A trip to Europe?

29:37.624 --> 29:38.457
No.

29:39.869 --> 29:41.637
Matching lip injections.

29:41.639 --> 29:44.902
Dr. Burke has a cancellation,
he can do us both now.

29:46.319 --> 29:48.912
I don't want lip injections.

29:49.979 --> 29:51.952
It's virtually a painless procedure.

29:52.259 --> 29:53.622
Just right at the top.

29:54.039 --> 29:56.217
Never mind, I'm gonna go wait outside.

29:56.219 --> 29:57.997
Wait, it'll be years before you

29:57.999 --> 29:59.549
can afford something like this.

30:00.699 --> 30:01.787
It's my treat.

30:01.789 --> 30:02.622
No, Mom.

30:04.432 --> 30:06.052
You never listen.

30:06.459 --> 30:09.002
I don't want it, God, no wonder Dad left.

30:14.343 --> 30:18.593
That's not why he left.

30:22.519 --> 30:23.350
Hey.

30:23.352 --> 30:24.185
Can I come in.

30:28.869 --> 30:30.819
I'm sorry, I'm sorry, it's not funny.

30:30.879 --> 30:31.710
What is wrong with her?

30:31.712 --> 30:33.107
She's fucking crazy.

30:33.109 --> 30:34.402
Hey, hey, easy.

30:34.799 --> 30:36.792
Go easy on her, okay?

30:37.379 --> 30:39.907
Someday, way before you're
ready, she'll be gone

30:39.909 --> 30:41.257
and you'll regret all the shitty things

30:41.259 --> 30:43.882
you said about her, believe me.

30:47.309 --> 30:49.277
Anyway, I'm sure she only
wants the best for you.

30:49.279 --> 30:50.847
What is that supposed to mean?

30:50.849 --> 30:53.382
I don't know, it's just
what people say about parents.

30:53.919 --> 30:55.219
She probably does, though,

30:55.499 --> 30:57.072
just has no idea what that is.

30:57.482 --> 30:59.232
I just, I need to get outta here.

30:59.809 --> 31:01.251
You'll be on your
own before you know it.

31:01.253 --> 31:03.322
No, like I need to get outta here, now.

31:06.149 --> 31:07.617
Sorry about yesterday.

31:07.619 --> 31:08.452
I know.

31:10.162 --> 31:13.346
So we're cool, we're all good, right?

31:13.609 --> 31:14.442
Yeah.

31:14.672 --> 31:15.505
Awesome.

31:24.269 --> 31:26.119
Do you think I need lip injections?

31:26.889 --> 31:28.012
Absolutely not.

31:28.519 --> 31:29.932
No, definitely not.

31:33.342 --> 31:34.175
Uhhh.

31:35.180 --> 31:37.744
I mean, maybe a nose job, but
definitely not lip injections.

31:37.746 --> 31:38.577
What?

31:38.579 --> 31:39.862
I'm kidding.

31:40.309 --> 31:41.140
I was kidding.

31:41.142 --> 31:42.997
- You're an asshole.
- It was a joke.

31:42.999 --> 31:45.717
Just kidding around, come
on, you know you're beautiful.

31:45.719 --> 31:47.502
I mean, you know what I mean.

31:48.162 --> 31:50.662
I'm sure guys your age
find you very pretty.

31:53.212 --> 31:54.045
Thanks.

31:54.999 --> 31:55.832
Of course.

31:58.659 --> 32:01.702
Ah, this should be it right here.

32:04.749 --> 32:05.582
Shit.

32:07.899 --> 32:10.549
I can't believe it, I used
to come here all the time.

32:12.149 --> 32:12.982
Can I drive?

32:14.039 --> 32:15.439
Where, where you wanna go?

32:16.233 --> 32:17.442
It's a surprise.

32:18.888 --> 32:19.888
All right.

32:20.153 --> 32:20.986
Switch.

32:29.371 --> 32:30.204
Careful.

32:55.499 --> 32:58.249
So what are you gonna do
when you finish your thesis?

32:59.949 --> 33:01.502
Teach, I guess.

33:02.611 --> 33:03.444
You guess?

33:05.716 --> 33:06.816
There aren't a lotta

33:07.739 --> 33:09.862
job listings for philosophers these days.

33:11.209 --> 33:13.109
Is that why you went to grad school?

33:15.629 --> 33:17.792
I did it honestly,

33:19.229 --> 33:20.812
because I didn't know what else to do.

33:22.559 --> 33:23.767
Which is why you should take the time now

33:23.769 --> 33:25.369
to figure that out for yourself.

33:26.229 --> 33:27.062
Or,

33:28.809 --> 33:31.392
focus on painting.

33:31.699 --> 33:34.127
My mom thinks I'd be
crazy to try and make

33:34.129 --> 33:35.792
a living as an artist.

33:36.949 --> 33:40.952
She says there's too many
talented people out there,

33:41.318 --> 33:42.518
and who am I to make it?

33:43.974 --> 33:45.324
That portrait that I saw?

33:46.019 --> 33:47.146
It was great.

33:48.398 --> 33:49.231
Really?

33:49.319 --> 33:50.152
Yeah.

33:51.388 --> 33:53.305
You're really talented.

33:53.442 --> 33:55.842
Well you're like the
only person that gets me.

33:58.279 --> 33:59.479
I doubt that.

34:04.099 --> 34:05.099
This place is great.

34:06.151 --> 34:06.984
It's nice.

34:09.119 --> 34:10.237
My dad used to bring me here

34:10.239 --> 34:12.862
whenever he needed to
get away from my mom.

34:14.029 --> 34:15.822
So this was a regular thing?

34:17.039 --> 34:18.688
Yeah, it was pretty much daily.

34:24.469 --> 34:26.192
Now he won't even call me back.

34:29.348 --> 34:30.848
Do you miss him?

34:32.268 --> 34:33.369
I get why he left.

34:36.018 --> 34:36.851
Right.

34:38.416 --> 34:40.083
But do you miss him?

34:42.649 --> 34:43.681
Yeah, I guess.

34:46.139 --> 34:48.092
I don't know, I don't really feel much.

34:53.380 --> 34:55.456
It's none of my business.

34:55.458 --> 34:57.722
But even if he doesn't
wanna be with your mom,

34:58.894 --> 35:00.644
he is still your dad.

35:01.456 --> 35:03.857
So he should be there for you.

35:13.995 --> 35:16.578
You're not supposed to do that.

35:16.985 --> 35:17.818
I know.

36:35.344 --> 36:37.594
You really are beautiful.

36:39.896 --> 36:44.012
You did say guys my age
would find me very pretty.

36:45.892 --> 36:48.676
You know what I meant.

37:33.629 --> 37:35.579
Where the hell have you been?

37:36.109 --> 37:36.942
Out.

37:37.209 --> 37:39.192
Out is not an answer!

37:39.769 --> 37:41.362
What do you want from me?

37:41.709 --> 37:44.047
When I stay in, you complain
that I don't go out enough,

37:44.049 --> 37:45.797
and when I do go out, you give me shit.

37:45.799 --> 37:47.722
It is one o'clock in the morning.

37:48.749 --> 37:50.187
You wouldn't care if you'd gone out,

37:50.189 --> 37:52.142
but since you look like that.

37:55.736 --> 37:57.147
You're not going anywhere until you

37:57.149 --> 37:58.512
tell me where you've been.

37:59.200 --> 38:01.076
To Evan's okay, can I go now?

38:27.137 --> 38:27.970
Please.

38:28.061 --> 38:29.144
Come on, Dad.

38:30.910 --> 38:32.436
Pick up.

38:32.438 --> 38:34.521
Pick up, please, come on.

38:36.899 --> 38:38.102
You've reached Dan.

39:33.695 --> 39:36.278
Can't stop thinking about it.

39:37.241 --> 39:39.824
I can't stop thinking about it.

39:41.933 --> 39:42.766
Hmmm.

39:45.599 --> 39:46.432
Hello?

39:48.028 --> 39:49.262
Vince?

39:50.669 --> 39:51.662
Hello?

39:53.879 --> 39:54.712
Hi.

39:54.880 --> 39:55.713
Hey.

40:03.039 --> 40:03.992
You've been busy.

40:04.139 --> 40:06.489
So Lizzy's coming to
get her stuff this week.

40:06.719 --> 40:08.367
She's gonna kill me if the
place still looks like this.

40:08.369 --> 40:10.567
Can you, can you take those pictures

40:10.569 --> 40:12.147
down over there and put them in a box?

40:12.149 --> 40:13.149
Get started on that?

40:16.569 --> 40:17.402
Sure.

40:24.378 --> 40:25.211
Coming.

40:29.519 --> 40:30.352
Evan.

40:31.209 --> 40:32.802
Sarah's not home right now.

40:32.929 --> 40:34.087
Oh, uh, sorry.

40:34.089 --> 40:36.072
Do you wanna come in for some lemonade?

40:36.269 --> 40:37.102
Come on in.

40:37.695 --> 40:38.528
Okay.

40:55.259 --> 40:58.802
So how long have
you and Sarah been an item?

41:00.255 --> 41:01.088
What?

41:01.469 --> 41:03.569
She told me you were very close.

41:06.269 --> 41:08.987
Yeah, she's been acting
kinda weird, to be honest.

41:08.989 --> 41:11.912
Oh, what do you mean?

41:12.470 --> 41:14.347
It's just that sometimes
I think she likes me,

41:14.349 --> 41:17.637
and then, I don't know, sometimes I don't.

41:17.639 --> 41:19.682
She's probably playing hard to get.

41:20.249 --> 41:21.857
She was in a great mood last night

41:21.859 --> 41:23.792
when she came home from your place.

41:25.647 --> 41:26.480
Uh, yeah.

41:28.449 --> 41:30.626
Thanks for the lemonade, but I gotta go.

41:31.309 --> 41:32.967
Come by, come back any time.

41:32.969 --> 41:35.022
- Yeah.
- Bye, Evan.

41:47.829 --> 41:49.532
Do you wanna get some food?

41:49.789 --> 41:51.589
You can order a pizza if you want.

41:53.719 --> 41:56.912
I was thinking maybe
we could drive somewhere.

41:57.529 --> 41:58.679
I gotta keep working.

42:00.969 --> 42:01.802
Okay.

42:03.189 --> 42:04.332
Then I'm gonna go.

42:05.037 --> 42:05.870
Okay.

42:10.249 --> 42:11.082
Bye.

42:11.217 --> 42:12.384
Bye.

42:29.597 --> 42:30.430
Ohhhhh.

