42:48.779 --> 42:51.842
Do you think you could
find someplace to go?

42:52.799 --> 42:54.422
Where am I supposed to go?

42:54.649 --> 42:56.232
Um, I don't know.

42:57.067 --> 42:58.567
What about Evan's?

43:00.100 --> 43:02.820
Thank you, honey, you're the best.

43:49.096 --> 43:49.932
You okay?

43:50.519 --> 43:51.352
Sorry.

43:53.149 --> 43:54.049
What's going on?

43:54.239 --> 43:55.072
Nothing.

43:58.820 --> 44:00.420
It's that older guy, isn't it?

44:01.389 --> 44:02.222
What?

44:02.749 --> 44:04.449
I was talking to your mom, and...

44:04.521 --> 44:06.307
What the fuck, why were
you talking to my mom?

44:06.309 --> 44:07.527
Because I went to see you,

44:07.529 --> 44:09.372
and you weren't there, as usual.

44:09.859 --> 44:11.267
And she said that you said you were at

44:11.269 --> 44:12.269
my house last night?

44:12.363 --> 44:14.842
Yeah, she was being a bitch,
and I didn't wanna go home.

44:15.969 --> 44:16.869
Do you like him?

44:17.249 --> 44:19.087
No, why would you even ask me that?

44:19.089 --> 44:20.177
Because you're always with him.

44:20.179 --> 44:22.792
Yeah, because we're just friends, okay?

44:23.409 --> 44:24.702
Look, don't go.

44:25.821 --> 44:27.592
I'm just worried about you.

44:28.009 --> 44:30.546
Don't worry about me,
and don't talk to my mom.

45:05.493 --> 45:06.326
Asshole.

45:14.684 --> 45:16.351
Mind if I come in?

45:16.505 --> 45:18.672
Yeah, of course.

45:38.699 --> 45:40.792
He totally blew me off.

45:41.569 --> 45:42.982
He didn't even call.

45:44.035 --> 45:45.085
Can you believe that?

45:46.579 --> 45:49.029
You deserve better, guy
sounds like an asshole.

45:50.009 --> 45:50.842
Thank you.

45:53.452 --> 45:55.232
What about you, Vincent?

45:56.129 --> 45:56.962
What about me?

45:57.919 --> 46:00.272
You must have girls
lined up around the block.

46:00.889 --> 46:02.772
I can assure you, there is no line.

46:03.946 --> 46:05.479
We're both adults here.

46:05.481 --> 46:07.536
I'm flattered, I am, but...

46:07.717 --> 46:08.548
Are you?

46:08.550 --> 46:09.542
Nancy? Are you listening?

46:14.319 --> 46:15.152
Coming.

46:19.359 --> 46:20.202
Sarah.

46:21.429 --> 46:22.262
Sarah?

46:23.769 --> 46:26.612
Mom? What are you doing here?

46:27.519 --> 46:28.902
Jacob stood me up.

46:28.959 --> 46:31.192
He's such a jerk.

46:31.789 --> 46:32.989
What are you doing here?

46:33.949 --> 46:36.099
You kicked me out of
the house, remember?

46:37.669 --> 46:39.942
What an imagination this one has.

46:40.239 --> 46:41.812
Come and sit with me.

46:42.869 --> 46:46.319
I am so glad that you and Vince are

46:46.856 --> 46:48.942
becoming such good friends.

46:49.319 --> 46:50.769
Why don't you have some wine?

46:51.669 --> 46:53.927
Vince, would you mind getting her a glass?

46:53.929 --> 46:54.762
Really?

46:56.736 --> 46:58.152
Uh, okay.

46:59.099 --> 47:02.112
Don't stay too long, I
think tonight's the night.

47:06.459 --> 47:09.792
Men just want younger women.

47:11.019 --> 47:14.507
It just doesn't matter how many crunches

47:14.509 --> 47:16.282
or down dogs you do.

47:19.573 --> 47:23.137
That's why I'm so glad you
finally have a boyfriend, honey.

47:23.139 --> 47:24.787
I don't have a boyfriend, Mom.

47:24.789 --> 47:25.937
Really, what about Evan?

47:25.939 --> 47:27.722
Evan's not my boyfriend.

47:28.989 --> 47:29.822
Well listen,

47:30.919 --> 47:33.142
you can only play hard to get for so long.

47:33.149 --> 47:34.509
Seriously, because

47:35.750 --> 47:37.652
you have to finally just grab one,

47:38.189 --> 47:40.149
hold on tight, because

47:42.409 --> 47:44.859
if you don't, you just go
through other people's,

47:45.689 --> 47:47.397
you know, leftovers, right?

47:47.399 --> 47:49.082
I'm talking to you too, Vincent.

47:49.369 --> 47:50.827
Let's go home, okay?

47:50.829 --> 47:52.902
I'm conversating with Vincent.

48:02.533 --> 48:04.737
I don't like
Evan, he's not my boyfriend.

48:04.739 --> 48:05.660
It's fine, it's fine,

48:05.662 --> 48:07.190
and you're talking too loudly.

48:07.192 --> 48:10.832
I mean, I only said that
to cover for the other night.

48:10.971 --> 48:11.804
Whisper.

48:11.959 --> 48:13.186
I don't like him.

48:14.169 --> 48:15.086
I like you.

48:18.789 --> 48:21.862
Sarah, I like you too, but it's just...

48:21.943 --> 48:24.032
It's fine, God, she's out cold.

48:25.709 --> 48:27.707
Sarah, Sarah, please, come here.

48:27.709 --> 48:28.542
Stop.

48:29.218 --> 48:31.945
Sarah, please don't.

48:33.599 --> 48:36.766
It's not funny, it's not funny, Sarah.

48:38.268 --> 48:39.706
Will you come back down here please?

48:39.708 --> 48:42.717
Sarah, come on, Sarah.

48:42.719 --> 48:44.222
Sarah, Sarah.

48:44.859 --> 48:45.692
I'm serious.

48:46.749 --> 48:48.022
Sarah, get outta the bed.

48:48.676 --> 48:51.189
This is not, this is not funny.

48:58.417 --> 48:59.584
Oh, my head.

49:06.679 --> 49:08.002
Oh God.

49:09.189 --> 49:10.022
Oh God.

49:23.633 --> 49:26.792
Hello?

49:28.048 --> 49:29.198
Hello, is anybody here?

49:31.286 --> 49:32.119
Oh, God.

49:37.515 --> 49:39.182
Sarah, stop, stop.

49:39.452 --> 49:41.017
She can't hear us.

49:50.390 --> 49:51.223
Hello?

49:54.789 --> 49:58.092
Ohhh, oh my God.

50:01.234 --> 50:04.395
You're talking too loud,
what's wrong with you?

50:04.397 --> 50:07.589
It's not fucking funny, it's not a joke.

50:19.316 --> 50:20.147
That was hot.

50:20.149 --> 50:21.202
Let's do it again.

50:21.791 --> 50:23.624
You have to go home.

50:24.908 --> 50:28.377
You have to go, Sarah,
you have to go home.

50:32.079 --> 50:32.912
Hey.

50:35.639 --> 50:37.992
Here, take these.

50:38.190 --> 50:39.562
Thank you.

50:39.564 --> 50:41.302
They'll make
you feel a lot better.

50:42.479 --> 50:44.229
Thank you, sweetie.

51:04.362 --> 51:07.852
What am I gonna do when
you go off to college?

51:08.919 --> 51:10.440
I haven't even applied yet, Mom.

51:10.442 --> 51:12.222
When you move to Silver Lake.

51:13.249 --> 51:15.049
I'm not gonna move to Silver Lake.

51:15.929 --> 51:17.952
You're gonna do a lot of fun things.

51:19.579 --> 51:21.179
And I'm gonna be here all alone.

51:22.446 --> 51:24.096
Mom, you're not gonna be alone.

51:29.419 --> 51:32.219
I'm really sorry about the
way things have turned out.

51:34.561 --> 51:36.111
Sometimes I think I could have,

51:36.889 --> 51:39.322
we could have tried a little harder.

51:40.175 --> 51:41.957
Mom, you guys fought all the time.

51:41.959 --> 51:42.809
I know.

51:43.019 --> 51:44.347
It's better with him gone.

51:44.349 --> 51:46.322
Yeah, I guess.

51:49.109 --> 51:50.282
We're doing okay, huh?

51:59.439 --> 52:01.942
Hope I didn't embarrass
you too much last night.

52:06.709 --> 52:07.542
It's okay.

52:11.299 --> 52:12.132
Hey.

52:12.169 --> 52:14.052
Hi, how's she doing?

52:15.029 --> 52:17.152
She keeps telling me she has a migraine,

52:17.379 --> 52:19.362
as if I don't know what a hangover is.

52:20.639 --> 52:22.997
She wants to live in a
world where you never grow up.

52:22.999 --> 52:24.242
But I am grown up.

52:30.269 --> 52:32.392
I thought you weren't
coming until tomorrow.

52:33.025 --> 52:35.522
Got tired of play dates, so
I thought I'd just stop by.

52:36.649 --> 52:39.192
I hope I'm not interrupting something.

52:39.679 --> 52:40.932
No, no, of course not.

52:42.439 --> 52:46.062
This is Sarah, she's been
helping clean out the house.

52:47.579 --> 52:50.922
Hi, I'm Elizabeth, I'm his sister.

52:51.379 --> 52:53.852
Sarah is Nancy's daughter.

52:54.579 --> 52:56.279
Nancy, next-door-neighbor Nancy?

52:57.959 --> 53:00.337
Yeah, yeah, she's been a huge help

53:00.339 --> 53:01.439
packing everything up.

53:03.949 --> 53:04.912
I brought lunch.

53:05.609 --> 53:06.559
You should join us.

53:06.949 --> 53:08.352
No, it's okay.

53:11.609 --> 53:12.452
Yeah, yeah.

53:13.189 --> 53:14.762
Of course, stay.

53:29.329 --> 53:31.279
I can't believe Mom held on to these.

53:32.029 --> 53:33.982
She pretty much held on to everything.

53:34.049 --> 53:34.882
I would know.

53:36.539 --> 53:37.992
What's that supposed to mean?

53:40.219 --> 53:41.052
Nothing.

53:43.749 --> 53:46.032
So, Sarah, you got to Findlay?

53:46.189 --> 53:47.022
Yeah.

53:47.389 --> 53:49.282
And you're a junior?

53:49.679 --> 53:51.679
I'm going into my junior high.

53:52.049 --> 53:54.222
So that makes you how old?

53:55.239 --> 53:56.072
16.

53:57.139 --> 53:57.972
16?

54:09.699 --> 54:10.532
Thanks again.

54:11.559 --> 54:12.509
See you tomorrow.

54:18.559 --> 54:19.392
Hey.

54:19.419 --> 54:20.822
What are you doing here?

54:20.869 --> 54:22.487
We're just having some lunch.

54:22.489 --> 54:23.452
What's with you?

54:23.699 --> 54:25.849
Okay, well, I'll just
leave you two then.

54:25.899 --> 54:28.187
Come, stop, join us.

54:28.189 --> 54:29.287
I'm not hungry.

54:29.289 --> 54:31.647
I told you not to talk to my mom.

54:31.649 --> 54:33.132
Well I came to see you.

54:33.689 --> 54:34.862
Stop!

54:36.127 --> 54:38.392
You sure stare at him a
lot for a guy you don't like.

54:38.658 --> 54:39.852
You're just jealous.

54:40.779 --> 54:42.747
What is with you, are
you like in love with him?

54:42.749 --> 54:44.142
Yeah, maybe I am.

54:46.269 --> 54:47.102
Wow.

54:47.749 --> 54:48.987
Yeah, it's even worse than I thought.

54:48.989 --> 54:50.127
I didn't mean it.

54:50.129 --> 54:51.862
He hates me anyway.

54:51.949 --> 54:53.199
Yeah, whatever you say.

54:53.909 --> 54:55.917
What are you even doing here anyway?

54:55.919 --> 54:58.992
Can't you take a hint
that I don't like you?

55:02.563 --> 55:04.763
You know, you've
turned into a real bitch.

55:10.989 --> 55:12.389
Are you sleeping with her?

55:12.429 --> 55:14.732
Jesus Christ, of course I'm not.

55:19.289 --> 55:22.966
Things might have gone two far once or...

55:23.289 --> 55:25.127
Have you completely lost your mind?

55:25.129 --> 55:26.362
It's been tough here,

55:26.989 --> 55:28.894
alone, surrounded by all this shit, okay?

55:28.896 --> 55:29.834
Here we go again.

55:29.836 --> 55:31.378
What the fuck is that
supposed to mean, Lizzie?

55:31.380 --> 55:33.964
There's always some girl who
adores you, and you love it,

55:33.966 --> 55:36.297
and then eventually they
find out that you're only

55:36.299 --> 55:38.397
with them because you're
terrified of being alone.

55:38.399 --> 55:40.199
It's time you figured your shit out.

55:40.329 --> 55:42.592
I'm sorry, you're one to talk.

55:42.779 --> 55:44.677
Because I've been here
taking care of all this shit

55:44.679 --> 55:46.282
on my own, actually.

55:46.359 --> 55:47.867
I did the funeral.

55:47.869 --> 55:48.917
And I offered to help!

55:48.919 --> 55:51.117
Well, yes, but I had to do it quickly

55:51.119 --> 55:53.819
and I couldn't just wait and
see if you would show up!

56:00.079 --> 56:01.519
I fucked up, I know.

56:04.649 --> 56:05.549
You just need to

56:06.589 --> 56:07.506
talk to...

56:08.149 --> 56:08.982
Sarah.

56:10.029 --> 56:12.809
And tell Sarah that you made a mistake

56:12.839 --> 56:14.802
and that you're sorry.

56:17.689 --> 56:19.839
You're leaving in a
few days anyway, right?

56:24.239 --> 56:25.794
Vince, are you listening to me?

56:25.796 --> 56:27.992
Yes, I heard you, I'm listening.

56:30.040 --> 56:30.873
It has to end.

56:31.699 --> 56:32.532
I know.

56:51.602 --> 56:52.769
Can we talk?

56:52.943 --> 56:53.972
Yes, definitely.

56:54.149 --> 56:56.307
I don't know what's going
on, but you were acting

56:56.309 --> 56:57.917
really weird last night, and then you just

56:57.919 --> 56:59.632
slammed the door in my face.

56:59.692 --> 57:01.109
I know, I know.

57:01.684 --> 57:02.851
And I'm sorry.

57:04.659 --> 57:05.812
I forgive you.

57:08.419 --> 57:10.322
Can we just hang out today?

57:19.420 --> 57:20.420
It's Evan.

57:20.739 --> 57:23.562
Evan, I thought you were upstairs?

57:24.429 --> 57:25.629
I need to talk to you.

57:27.240 --> 57:28.071
Oh my gosh.

57:28.073 --> 57:30.129
Okay, Sarah, just
listen to me one second.

57:30.169 --> 57:31.657
I don't know how to say this, but...

57:31.659 --> 57:32.759
Let's talk tomorrow.

57:37.252 --> 57:39.552
Just one kiss, and then we'll talk.

57:57.039 --> 57:59.039
Fuck, oh my God, fuck.

57:59.589 --> 58:00.422
We,

58:01.699 --> 58:03.712
we, we can't do this anymore.

58:04.789 --> 58:06.192
No one's gonna find out.

58:06.419 --> 58:07.252
That's not it.

58:08.609 --> 58:10.589
I know that you're leaving, but

58:10.979 --> 58:13.757
I can come visit you or you can come back.

58:13.759 --> 58:15.002
No, no, this,

58:15.056 --> 58:17.552
Sarah, this should have
never happened, okay?

58:19.191 --> 58:20.352
You don't mean that.

58:20.489 --> 58:22.017
I do, I do.

58:22.019 --> 58:23.992
Of course I do, I'm 36 years old.

58:24.159 --> 58:25.202
And you're 16.

58:25.402 --> 58:26.233
So?

58:26.235 --> 58:27.066
So?

58:27.068 --> 58:28.667
This is your time to
make mistakes, not mine.

58:28.669 --> 58:30.517
It's my time to get my shit together.

58:30.519 --> 58:32.507
Doesn't feel like a mistake to me.

58:32.509 --> 58:34.347
Sarah, this doesn't make any sense.

58:34.349 --> 58:35.999
This can't ever be anything more.

58:41.070 --> 58:41.903
Oh.

58:43.976 --> 58:46.337
I'm,

58:46.339 --> 58:47.702
I'm sorry, I am.

58:49.739 --> 58:51.089
I never wanted to hurt you.

58:54.279 --> 58:55.112
Hey, hey.

58:56.939 --> 58:59.612
You're an amazing girl, you are.

59:00.636 --> 59:02.336
And you have so much ahead of you.

59:05.901 --> 59:07.412
But I can't be a part of it.

59:09.646 --> 59:10.479
I'm sorry.

59:12.439 --> 59:14.292
Sarah, I'm sorry.

59:16.822 --> 59:17.655
Fuck.

59:26.899 --> 59:28.512
Hold it, right there.

59:29.689 --> 59:32.002
Stop, we need to talk!

59:32.809 --> 59:34.206
We need to talk!

59:35.384 --> 59:36.217
Stop!

59:44.092 --> 59:45.842
Sarah, open the door.

59:50.934 --> 59:53.267
Sarah, open the door please.

01:01:30.496 --> 01:01:31.732
How could you?

01:01:32.029 --> 01:01:33.267
I trusted you.

01:01:33.269 --> 01:01:34.367
I tried to stop it.

01:01:34.369 --> 01:01:36.502
Oh come on, she's a child.

01:01:41.239 --> 01:01:42.718
I never meant for this to happen.

01:01:42.720 --> 01:01:44.111
You should be ashamed of yourself.

01:01:44.113 --> 01:01:44.944
Believe me, I am.

01:01:44.946 --> 01:01:45.777
Stop!

01:01:45.779 --> 01:01:46.697
Honey, be quiet, shh.

01:01:46.699 --> 01:01:47.592
Be quiet.

01:01:48.029 --> 01:01:48.860
Sarah...

01:01:48.862 --> 01:01:49.852
Don't say her name!

01:01:49.869 --> 01:01:52.172
Mom, can I talk to Vince alone?

01:01:52.379 --> 01:01:53.335
No that is not gonna happen.

01:01:53.337 --> 01:01:54.168
Please?

01:01:54.170 --> 01:01:55.001
It's not gonna happen.

01:01:55.003 --> 01:01:55.834
- No, honey, no.
- Please?

01:01:55.836 --> 01:01:57.789
- Go inside now.
- Mom!

01:02:03.609 --> 01:02:05.812
Your mother would be horrified.

01:02:25.229 --> 01:02:26.602
Leave me alone.

01:02:26.749 --> 01:02:30.255
Sarah, honey,
you need to open the door.

01:02:30.257 --> 01:02:32.217
Just leave me alone, please.

01:02:32.219 --> 01:02:33.719
Sarah, please open the door.

01:02:40.783 --> 01:02:41.616
Awww.

01:02:49.759 --> 01:02:50.602
I'm so sorry.

01:02:54.989 --> 01:02:58.452
I know it hurts like hell right now.

01:02:59.657 --> 01:03:01.782
But this will pass.

01:03:02.316 --> 01:03:04.052
How can you say that?

01:03:04.349 --> 01:03:05.347
Mom, I love him.

01:03:05.349 --> 01:03:07.177
I know, I know, I know you love him.

01:03:07.179 --> 01:03:09.229
It wouldn't hurt this much if you didn't.

01:03:12.423 --> 01:03:13.623
But you'll get over him.

01:03:15.028 --> 01:03:17.456
No, I'm not as strong as you.

01:03:19.233 --> 01:03:20.812
What are you talking about?

01:03:20.962 --> 01:03:23.022
I can't just bounce back like you do.

01:03:24.439 --> 01:03:26.107
Oh, oh, okay.

01:03:26.109 --> 01:03:28.522
Well, that takes years of training.

01:03:30.939 --> 01:03:32.902
You get better at it as you get older.

01:03:35.129 --> 01:03:36.819
But it does still hurt,

01:03:38.119 --> 01:03:38.952
every time.

01:03:40.099 --> 01:03:41.372
I never see it.

01:03:42.889 --> 01:03:44.682
Well, I don't want you to see it.

01:03:45.259 --> 01:03:47.162
I don't want you worrying about me.

01:03:50.055 --> 01:03:50.892
I'm sorry.

01:03:52.732 --> 01:03:55.149
You don't need to be sorry.

01:03:57.142 --> 01:03:59.210
You're gonna be all right.

01:04:01.787 --> 01:04:03.801
You're gonna be just fine.

01:04:45.720 --> 01:04:46.827
Jesus Christ.

01:04:46.829 --> 01:04:48.996
Sarah, what are you doing?

01:04:49.992 --> 01:04:51.409
You're leaving?

01:04:53.289 --> 01:04:55.989
I know this doesn't make
any sense to you right now.

01:04:56.239 --> 01:04:58.922
I do, but that's how it has to be.

01:05:00.549 --> 01:05:02.312
I didn't tell her, I swear.

01:05:03.349 --> 01:05:07.362
Sarah, you didn't do anything
wrong, this is my fault.

01:05:25.194 --> 01:05:26.027
Sarah?

01:05:27.231 --> 01:05:28.148
Look at me.

01:05:30.256 --> 01:05:32.256
Stick with the painting.

01:05:32.711 --> 01:05:34.044
I mean it, okay?

01:05:35.250 --> 01:05:36.083
I will.

01:05:38.539 --> 01:05:40.223
And give your mom a break.

01:05:40.225 --> 01:05:42.308
She really does love you.

01:05:43.046 --> 01:05:43.963
I'll try.

01:05:53.390 --> 01:05:54.557
I should go.

01:06:18.028 --> 01:06:18.945
Bye, Sarah.

01:08:16.437 --> 01:08:17.937
Gosh, I'm sorry.

01:08:18.312 --> 01:08:19.792
You really need to get
your hearing checked.

01:08:23.679 --> 01:08:24.511
Is that me?

01:08:28.157 --> 01:08:28.990
Yeah.

01:08:33.926 --> 01:08:35.260
How wonderful.

01:08:37.515 --> 01:08:39.915
Could you make me look a
little more attractive?

01:08:41.398 --> 01:08:42.898
That's my style.

01:08:44.104 --> 01:08:45.437
You know what?

01:08:46.604 --> 01:08:48.604
Oh gosh, I just love it.

01:08:50.385 --> 01:08:51.218
